{"title":"江南雨","authors":["洪三泰"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":3,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广东湛江农垦局  洪三泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑沉沉的天宇里禁锢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是被严寒冻结的泪珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然，那条通天的闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昭示着新生与光明的路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，洒落了，洒落了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作青春和生命的音符。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄地引起小苗的共鸣："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出土哟，快快出土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给大地的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大海的呐喊，春风的脚步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呵，刚刚洗净了世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便悄然地粉身碎骨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风走过，悄悄地、轻轻地……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿——多么明晰的足迹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏雨洗，洗不掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风刮，刮不起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬雪不敢来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只在江北窥伺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多慷慨大方的足迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给山，山绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给水，水碧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给苍天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一面蔚蓝的镜子……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}